{{Watchlist-messages|
{{RfA watchlist notice|format=watchlist|cookie=733}}
{{Display/watchlist
|from=April 28, 2026
|until=May 5, 2026
|cookie=740
|text=[[Wikipedia:WikiProject Guild of Copy Editors/Backlog elimination drives/May 2026#Signing up|'''Sign up here''']] for the month-long Guild of Copy Editors' May copy-editing drive. Have fun, improve articles, and earn barnstars!
}}
{{Display/watchlist
|from=29 April 2026
|until=5 May 2026
|cookie=741
|text=The '''[[Wikipedia:Administrator elections/May 2026/Candidates|nomination phase]]''' is now open in the May [[Wikipedia:Administrator elections/May 2026|administrator elections]]. Qualified users are encouraged to seek a nomination from an experienced peer. Self-nomination is also allowed. The nominations phase ends at 23:59 UTC on 5 May.
}}
{{Display/watchlist
 |from=29 April 2026
 |until=5 May 2026
 |cookie=742
 |text='''[[Wikipedia:New pages patrol/Backlog drives/May 2026#Signing up|Sign up now]]''' for the May New Pages Patrol backlog drive. Review articles and earn barnstars!
}}
